{"tid":1931174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲破天荒下達禁令 要求所有公民不要出國旅遊至少半年！","createTime":"2020-03-18T04:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T15:51:50.000Z","uid":63113,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"46d2ff7345d88dff72ac357a3e50b24695479db4","tid":1931174,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fabab9c13ddea152f48fbabd9d71caadbbf044","tid":1931174,"uid":63113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:40:37.000Z","msg":"為抑制2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，俗稱武漢肺炎）疫情擴散，澳洲總理莫里森今天下達史無前例的禁令，要求公民暫停國外旅行。此禁令實施無限期，可能至少6個月。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森（Scott Morrison）表示，武漢肺炎疫情是百年一遇的事件，「澳洲自第一次世界大戰以來就不曾見過這樣的事」。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森說：「我們要維持澳洲的運作與功能，但看起來可能會與正常情況有些出入。」他並警告，相關措施施行時間可能持續至少6個月。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲目前為止武漢肺炎確診病例超過450起，數字每天還在增加。而死亡病例累計5人。<br />\n<br />\n然而，莫里森婉拒比照其他國家讓學校停課，說這麼做對社會與經濟所造成的衝擊將會「很嚴重」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/firstnews/202003180041.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202003180041.aspx&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=d86e6bd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/firstnews/202003180041.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"2354dd57f1c2b5d579f4d950254d59ccec4933f8","tid":1931174,"uid":69746,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"正 希望個個國家都咁做 航空 旅遊 酒店 全面仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19dcf50b403ac1972a84645a98a727075adf014","tid":1931174,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6f8Aor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6f8Aor.gif&h=f06aa0bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為抑制武漢肺炎疫情擴散，澳洲總理莫里森18日下達史無前例的禁令，要求公民暫停國外旅行。圖為雪梨歌劇院前民眾戴上口罩。"},{"pid":"f2473fa90b13b60d7c76522df7a49aa5262e